 The heater boxes are G and H in this pic:
 http://www.bus-boys.com/Pg33.html

 They are your exhaust manifolds, so you cannot remove them completely.

 Best suggestion for your problem would be to find a 411/412 with the gas
heater and get the mini heater boxes off of it. They are very compact.

Or put in hydraulic lifters.....


